WEBVTT

00:01:29.463 --> 00:01:31.681
But that, too, became too complicated.

00:01:32.559 --> 00:01:35.504
Robert became fearful and withdrawn.

00:01:36.281 --> 00:01:38.662
A year and a half later,
he started hearing voices

00:01:38.686 --> 00:01:40.883
and believing that people
were following him.

00:01:40.907 --> 00:01:43.629
Doctors diagnosed him with schizophrenia,

00:01:43.653 --> 00:01:45.773
and they gave him
the best drug they could.

00:01:45.797 --> 00:01:48.805
That drug makes the voices
somewhat quieter,

00:01:48.829 --> 00:01:52.818
but it didn't restore his bright mind
or his social connectedness.

00:01:54.270 --> 00:01:56.126
Robert struggled to remain connected

00:01:56.150 --> 00:01:59.007
to the worlds of school
and work and friends.

00:01:59.031 --> 00:02:00.414
He drifted away,